Saudi lifts Sept Arab Light crude formula to Asia . Saudi Arabia has said it will raise its September - lifting crude oil price formula to Asian customers by 10 cents per barrel for both Arab Light and Berri Extra Light , traders said on Tuesday . Saudi Arabia has also told its Asian customers that it will raise its September - lifting crude oil price formula for Arab Medium and Arab Heavy by 20 cents per barrel , they said . The September term crude price for Arab Light was set at the Oman / Dubai average plus 10 cents per barrel , traders said . 
